<p>We will also be using an interactive textbook called <strong><em>How to Think Like a Computer Scientist</em></strong>. To access the textbook, please do the following:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Go to <strong><a href="http://interactivepython.org/" target="_blank">interactivepython.org</a></strong></li>
  <li>Register for an account (or sign in via Facebook, Twitter, Google).</li>
  <li>Input your account details. The Course Name is &ldquo;<strong>GalileoAOIT</strong>&rdquo; (no space).</li>
  <li>You should be able to access the textbook now. The first chapter is &ldquo;The Way of the Program.&rdquo;</li>
  <li>Begin reading &ldquo;<strong>The Way of the Program</strong>&rdquo; and complete the exercises in the chapter. You&rsquo;ll notice that there are questions you can check and examples you can run inside the textbook!</li>
</ol>
